Fast Track is a monthly information technology magazine published by 9.9 MediaWorx Pvt. Ltd and distributed along with Digit. It is an in-depth reference guide to any given sub-topic of information technology, such as web publishing and open source software, or a product. The detail in the Fast Track series ranges from the beginner to the intermediate and often with references to advanced content.
